            int interest,
            java.util.ArrayList<Product> products)
        User constructor for database retrievals overloaded with userID, interest count, and ArrayList of Products.
        Parameters:
        userID - The primary key ID of this user.
        uscEmail - The uscEmail corresponding to this user.
        password - The password for this user.
        fName - The first name of this user.
        lName - The last name of this user.
        photoPath - The filepath of this user's profile photo.
        interest - The amount of total interest this user has attained as a seller across all of their products.
        products - ArrayList of Product objects which this user is selling.
